ca.ualberta.cmput301f18t11.medicam.models

Class Patient

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.ualberta.cmput301f18t11.medicam.models.abstracts.PersistedModel
      • ca.ualberta.cmput301f18t11.medicam.models.abstracts.User
        • ca.ualberta.cmput301f18t11.medicam.models.Patient
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Patient
extends User
    Represents a patient that uses this app to record their various medical problems.

    The problems are held as a Collection of String uuids that uniquely represent every individual Problem object that is associated with this patient. Each patient can also record a front-facing and back-facing full-body photo to use to point out where on their body each problem is occurring. These photo each have a uri String that is stored so that the photo can be retrieved when needed.
